  "body": "**Is your feature request related to a problem? Please describe.**\r\nIn our workflows (`hive_tests` and `hive_consensus_tests`) we are preparing docker images and then running hive tests. Recently there was added `Dockerfile.git` file to base hive repo (https://github.com/ethereum/hive/blob/master/clients/nethermind/Dockerfile.git) which makes it possible to skip the step of preparing docker images. We can simplify our workflows now.\r\n",
